{"tid":2025080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[號外] 中國4月進口急跌14.2%","createTime":"2020-05-20T04:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T06:52:58.000Z","uid":66087,"like":72,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"c04e016e7f0f22c6d56352824619c169a4803d17","tid":2025080,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T04:16:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5603/4546497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5603%2F4546497&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krEXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=bb9006af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5603/4546497</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國4月出口數據交出意外成績，以美元計，中國4月出口年增3.5%，遠高出預期的-15.7%。<br />\n<br />\n進口則年減14.2%，比預期的-12.4%更差。<br />\n<br />\n2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，武漢肺炎）疫情在全球蔓延，全球主要經濟體大多實行了嚴格的隔離防疫措施，外界預期將對中國外貿帶來嚴峻的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n中國海關總署今天在官網公布4月外貿數據，出口意外地由負轉正。以美元計，中國4月出口2002.8億美元，年增3.5%；進口1549.4億美元，年減14.2%。當月貿易順差擴大至453.4億美元。"},{"pid":"b9e8587a19ab089ef525e5e250c2a857d4b5af13","tid":2025080,"uid":253016,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T04:17:50.000Z","msg":"食草時代來了"},{"pid":"212f54833cd0b806078a207af4451bb264137001","tid":2025080,"uid":41116,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T04:22:36.000Z","msg":"報復性消費..丫唔係 報復性收費來了"},{"pid":"0d89b455c539e2966cca2bae132b65a4ae25cdf5","tid":2025080,"uid":140953,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T04:22:55.000Z","msg":"中國人只買中國產品<br />\n又贏"},{"pid":"74779ba527ca3ed595bcbfc8e93d4e7aeca5a462","tid":2025080,"uid":202426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T04:23:48.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"56c937b4bc7cada13017965fde0409a53c03ee62","tid":2025080,"uid":58209,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T04:26:29.000Z","msg":"食草可活一年 唔怕"},{"pid":"64ad79d2f138de762f948ad0ad36f7d6255b64cb","tid":2025080,"uid":44358,"like":15,"dislike":2,"sc